      <title>随着奈拉暴跌，尼日利亚命令银行削减外汇敞口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/ngn-usd-nigeria-orders-banks-to-cut-forex-exposures-as-naira-plunges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行命令银行限制外汇敞口，以遏制金融体系风险，这是改善该国动荡的货币市场流动性的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/ngn-usd-nigeria-orders-banks-to-cut-forex-exposures-as-naira-plunges</guid>
