    <item>
      <title>Arc’teryx Maker 引导 IPO 股价低于每股 13 美元的区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/arc-teryx-maker-guides-ipo-share-pricing-below-range-at-13-each</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亚玛芬体育公司（Amer Sports Inc.）告诉潜在投资者，该公司正在考虑将其美国首次公开募股的股票定价低于市场定价范围。]]></description>
