    <item>
      <title>纽约社区银行 (NY Community Bancorp) 股价下跌 45%，创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-31/ny-community-bancorp-stock-drops-record-45-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年从 Signature Bank 购买存款的地区银行纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 在报告第四季度意外亏损并削减股息后，股价下跌了 45%，创历史新高。彭博社记者马努斯·克兰尼报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-31/ny-community-bancorp-stock-drops-record-45-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于新的银行担忧和美国经济数据，国债收益率暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/treasury-yields-slide-as-data-bolsters-fed-rate-cut-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债周三上涨，因数据显示招聘放缓速度快于预期，纽约一家银行公布意外亏损后股价暴跌，引发了人们对地区银行健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/treasury-yields-slide-as-data-bolsters-fed-rate-cut-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:44:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杠杆率达 2000% 的对冲基金引起欧盟监管机构的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/hedge-funds-with-2-000-leverage-are-catching-the-eu-s-attention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲监管机构正在密切关注一批持有抵押贷款债券且平均总杠杆率超过 2,000% 的对冲基金，其头寸规模之大可能会影响市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/hedge-funds-with-2-000-leverage-are-catching-the-eu-s-attention</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国增加季度债务销售，但预计不会再出现更多提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-increases-quarterly-debt-sale-sees-no-more-boosts-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部连续第三次提高了季度长期债券发行规模，并表示明年之前可能不会再增加发行规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-increases-quarterly-debt-sale-sees-no-more-boosts-coming</guid>
