      <title>纽约社区银行因意外亏损和股息削减而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/new-york-community-bancorp-slumps-on-surprise-loss-dividend-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 因信用质量恶化和股息削减而出现意外亏损，股价暴跌 46%，创历史新高。]]></description>
